         <div type="edition"
              ana="#b1"
              subtype="transcription"
              xml:id="hamm0031.transcription"
              corresp="#hamm0031.diplomatic #hamm0031.translation">
            <p>Αὐξίτω Πέργη,<lb/>
ἡ πρώτη<lb/>
τῆς Παμ<lb break="no"/>φυ<lb break="no"/>λί<lb break="no"/>ας.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation"
              xml:id="hamm0031.translation"
              corresp="#hamm0031.diplomatic #hamm0031.transcription">
            <p>Prosper <placeName>Perge</placeName>, the capital of <placeName>Pamphylia</placeName>!</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Slab of gray-white marble. Inscription is symmetrically arranged in the form of a triangle, with lines of decreasing length and widening margins. Script faces south.</p>
